snippet.title: SwSt 1 : an O-rich planetary nebula around a C-rich central star
snippet.description: SwSt 1 : an O-rich planetary nebula around a C-rich central star / De Marco, O ; Crowther, P A ; Barlow, M J ; Clayton, G C ; De Koter, A The hydrogen-deficient carbon-rich [WCL] type central star HD167362 and its oxygen-rich planetary nebula (PN) SwSt~1 are investigated.
